  "title": "3 day week (36hrs) min $1,600/mth Immediate: Casual Floater, Facilities & Operations Support",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<p>We're urgently hiring a dedicated and reliable Casual Floater for our Facilities Management team. This permanent part-time role offers a consistent 3-day work week for work-life balance and stable employment. You'll ensure the functionality, cleanliness, and safety of our premises.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>• Cleaning &amp; Housekeeping: Perform comprehensive cleaning, sanitization, waste disposal, and stock replenishment (offices, restrooms, common areas).</p>\n<p>• Light Maintenance &amp; Operations: Assist with basic repairs, system troubleshooting, event setup/tear-down, and minor administrative tasks.</p>\n<p>• Inventory Management: Monitor and report supply levels for cleaning materials, pantry items, and office consumables.</p>\n<p>• General Support: Execute diverse ad-hoc tasks for efficient facility operations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Work Arrangement:</p>\n<p>• Work Days: 3 days per week, 8-12 hour shifts (totalling 36 hours weekly). Specific days/shifts will be discussed.</p>\n<p>• Site Placement: Prioritized near your residence for convenience.</p>\n<p>• Reporting: Directly to the Site Manager of your assigned location.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidate Requirements:</p>\n<p>• Reliability: Consistently attends work and adheres to schedules.</p>\n<p>• Physical Aptitude: Capable of standing, walking, bending, and lifting reasonable handheld equipment.</p>\n<p>• Experience: Prior experience in cleaning, facilities management, general operations, or maintenance is advantageous.</p>\n<p>• Eligibility: Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Remuneration &amp; Benefits:</p>\n<p>• Gross Monthly Salary: SGD $1,600.</p>\n<p>• Approximate Take-Home: $10 per hour after mandatory CPF deductions.</p>\n<p>• Statutory CPF Contributions</p>\n<p>• Pro-rated Leave: Annual Leave and Sick Leave entitlements.</p>\n<p>• Public Holiday Pay.</p>\n<p>• Uniform Provided.</p>\n<p>• Training: Opportunities for on-the-job training and skill development in facilities management.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Application Process:</p>\n<p>This is an immediate and urgent opening. Submit your resume to hr@sun-city.com.sg without delay.</p>",
